Former President Goodluck Jonathan’s Senior Special Assistant on Public Affairs, Doyin Okupe, has said Dongaro leaves, Tumeric and hydroxychloroquine were amongst the medications he used to recover from coronavirus. He disclosed this on his twitter handle on Wednesday. None of our members were arrested with AK47 – IPOB React He said, ” My medications for covid19. Hydroxychloroquine 400mg 2ce dly for 2days then 400mg dly for 3days. Azithromycin 500mg fly  Zinc sulphate 100mg dly . VitzC 1200mg dly . ”I also supported wt mixture of ginger, garlic, tumeric & lemon. In kaduna they added dongoyaro leaves.  No global” “On the 23rd of April, my wife, Aduralere, and I tested positive for COVID-19. To the Glory of God, we were discharged this morning after obtaining two negative reports. I thank Almighty God for His Mercies,” he tweeted on Tuesday. He also added, ”There is no global consensus among scientists or medical experts on any one treatment regime. No credible scientific research document is presently available or acceptable for treatment of COVID-19. The key factor is the immune status of patients. Boost your immunity with known supplements. “If you must take hydroxychloroquine, please to speak to your doctor to confirm if you have any cardiac ARRHYTHMIAS. If you do, you need close monitoring before embarking on the use of these drugs. 90 to 95% of infected patients will go through, even without hospitalization. 90% of young people will survive attack,” he tweeted. Okupe and his wife, Aduralere, were recently discharged after spending about two weeks in a COVID-19 isolation and treatment centre in Sagamu, Ogun State. My medications for covid19.Hydroxychloroquine 400mg 2ce dly for 2days then 400mg dly for 3days.Azithromycin 500mg fly Zinc sulphate 100mg dly . VitzC 1200mg dly .I also supported wt mixture of ginger, garlic, tumeric & lemon. In kaduna they added dongoyaro leaves. No global